text: Win Min Than (; born 30 November 1933) is a Burmese-Australian actress. She is best known for her role in the 1954 Hollywood movie The Purple Plain. Than was born in Bago, Burma. Her career lasted from 1954 to 1957. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Burmese actors Category:Australian movie actors Category:Naturalised citizens of Australia
